    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Combining a refined aesthetic with proven mechanical integrity, the automobile offers an exceptional balance of performance and comfort. Every component has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal. We invite you to experience the enduring value and sophisticated engineering that define this distinguished model.",
      "price": 34900.0,
